notify(address,uint256,bool).details: The reconcile amount allows us to prevent diluting other users' rewards

params._maturities: Maturities of the series that we want to reconcile users on.

notify(address,uint256,bool).notice: Distribute the rewards tokens to the user according to their share

reconcile(address[],uint256[]).notice: Reconciles users target balances to zero by distributing rewards on their holdings, to avoid dilution of next Series' YT holders. This function should be called right after a Series matures and will save the user's YT balance (in target terms) on reconciledAmt[usr]. When `notify()` is triggered, we take that amount and subtract it from the user's target balance (`tBalance`) which will fix (or reconcile) his position to prevent dilution.
